Package: webPrices
Type: Package
Title: Screen scraping for collecting wholesale product pricing on web
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Burton Lueth III <burt.lueth@icloud.com> [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Burton Lueth III <burt.lueth@icloud.com>
Description: An implementation of scraping functions designed to extract and 
    tidy product and price information from online web stores. The package is 
    geared towards B2B markets and allows the aggregation of web pricing and
    product information in a tidy workflow across multiple online wholesalers
    including Home Depot, Amazon, and Lowes. 
License: GPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
Suggests: testthat
Imports: 
    rvest,
    tidyverse,
    stringr
